{
  "texts": [
    "Then, short skip connections are used to handle this problem.",
    "This process is known as the residual connections (He et al. 2016).",
    "The residual connection helps to mitigate the problem of vanishing gradient by allowing an alternative shortcut track for the gradient to flow through as shown in Fig. 29 the training of GANs.",
    "It also enhanced the feature exchanges across layers.",
    "The generated synthetic PET images are evaluated with the PSNR for image quality."
  ]
